  <brief_title>Effects of a Computerized Physician Order Entry (CPOE)-Based Inpatient Insulin Protocol on Glycemic Outcomes</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effects of a Computerized Physician Order Entry (CPOE)-Based Inpatient Insulin Protocol on Glycemic Outcomes</official_title>
